📖 Surah Al-Ikhlas (112)

🌟 Taruf:
Surah Al-Ikhlas Qur’an ki chhoti magar nihayat ahem surah hai. 
Isay Tawheed ki surah bhi kaha jata hai kyunki ye Allah Ta’ala ki zaat aur uski wahdaniyat (oneness) ko bayan karti hai.

_____________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

🌿 Ahmiyat:

Nabi ﷺ ne farmaya: “Ye surah Qur’an ka teesra hissa hai.” (Sahih Bukhari)
Rozana is surah ka tilawat karna protection aur ajar ka zariya hai.

_____________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

📝 Mufhoom (Summary):

1️⃣ Allah ek hai – us ka koi shareek nahi.
2️⃣ Woh sab ka sahara hai (As-Samad), sab us par depend karte hain.
3️⃣ Na uska koi walad hai na woh kisi ka walad hai.
4️⃣ Allah jaisa koi bhi nahi – woh mukammal, la-sharik aur be-misaal hai.

_____________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

📘 Lessons for us:

✨ Allah Ta’ala ki zaat mein shirk bilkul ghalat hai.
✨ Humein apni ibadat sirf Allah ke liye khalis karni chahiye.
✨ Allah par poora bharosa aur yaqeen rakhein.

_____________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

🌸 Short Reminder:
Surah Al-Ikhlas humein Allah ki ekta aur uski mukammal zaat ka paigham deti hai.
Ye surah humein shirk se bachne aur sirf Allah ki ibadat karne ki taleem deti hai.
